e date of such request.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Construction of section","label":"b Construction of section","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1983c/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1983c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs1983c%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Subsection (a) shall not be construed to supersede any duty imposed on the Secretary by any law or rule of law in effect immediately before , unless such duty is in direct conflict with any duty imposed by subsection (a).January 6, 1988","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
